summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 69E & 69W, page 165 & 166, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Steel Plant Addition, described as Lot 18, Block 3, Lots 19 and 20, Block 3 - less the south 200 ft. thereof - and Lot 11, Block 2, as Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone.
